{"id":1899,"date":"2025-03-05T13:59:34","date_gmt":"2025-03-05T13:59:34","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/wildact.k-tech-services.com\/?p=1899"},"modified":"2025-03-30T14:06:26","modified_gmt":"2025-03-30T14:06:26","slug":"cung-doi-cct-tuan-tra-xuyen-man-mua","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/vi\/cung-doi-cct-tuan-tra-xuyen-man-mua\/","title":{"rendered":"C\u00d9NG \u0110\u1ed8I CCT TU\u1ea6N TRA XUY\u00caN M\u00c0N M\u01afA"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>?\ufe0f D\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u01a1n m\u01b0a tr\u00e1i m\u00f9a, \u0110\u1ed9i C\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng Tu\u1ea7n tra B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 r\u1eebng (CCT &#8211; Community Conservation Team) \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ed9i m\u01b0a gi\u00f3, \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c tu\u1ea7n tra \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u00e1nh r\u1eebng Ch\u01b0 Yang Sin s\u1ea1ch b\u1eaby.<\/p>\n<p>?\ufe0f V\u1edbi 13 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00eam tu\u1ea7n tra d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p, c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i CTT ph\u1ea3i mang trang ph\u1ee5c \u01b0\u1edbt s\u0169ng do qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o ch\u01b0a k\u1ecbp kh\u00f4 th\u00ec l\u1ea1i m\u1eafc m\u01b0a tr\u00e1i m\u00f9a. M\u01b0a to m\u00f9 m\u1ecbt, khi\u1ebfn cho vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n d\u1ea5u v\u1ebft th\u1ee3 s\u0103n v\u00e0 b\u1eaby c\u00e0ng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00e0ng th\u00eam quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01a1n khi ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt hoang d\u00e3. Trong th\u00e1ng 2, \u0111\u1ed9i CCT \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c tu\u1ea7n tra b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 r\u1eebng:<br \/>\n? 85km tu\u1ea7n tra r\u1eebng gi\u00e0 Ch\u01b0 Yang Sin<br \/>\n?\ufe0f 64 gi\u1edd tu\u1ea7n tra xuy\u00ean m\u00e0n m\u01b0a<br \/>\n? 286 b\u1eaby \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e1o g\u1ee1<br \/>\n?\ufe0f 2 l\u00e1n tr\u1ea1i tr\u00e1i ph\u00e9p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e1o d\u1ee1<\/p>\n<p>? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i CCT g\u00ecn gi\u1eef nh\u1eefng c\u00e1nh r\u1eebng gi\u00e0 v\u00e0 thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean hoang d\u00e3 t\u1ea1i Ch\u01b0 Yang Sin, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n b\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n \u0111a d\u1ea1ng sinh h\u1ecdc cho n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0, cho ch\u00ednh ch\u00fang ta v\u00e0 cho th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 mai sau.<\/p>\n<p>? N\u1ed8I DUNG CHUY\u1ec2N KHO\u1ea2N:<br \/>\nS25CCT &#8211; Donate to WildAct<br \/>\nK\u00e8m m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p g\u1eedi t\u1eb7ng \u0111\u1ed9i CCT n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n.<\/p>\n<p>? Th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n kho\u1ea3n:<br \/>\nNg\u00e2n h\u00e0ng TMCP K\u1ef9 Th\u01b0\u01a1ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam (Techcombank)<br \/>\nTT HANH DONG VI DV HOANG DA VN<br \/>\n19133451997018<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>?\ufe0f D\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u01a1n m\u01b0a tr\u00e1i m\u00f9a, \u0110\u1ed9i C\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng Tu\u1ea7n tra B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 r\u1eebng (CCT &#8211; Community Conservation Team) \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ed9i m\u01b0a gi\u00f3, \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c tu\u1ea7n tra \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u00e1nh r\u1eebng Ch\u01b0 Yang Sin s\u1ea1ch b\u1eaby. ?\ufe0f V\u1edbi 13 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00eam tu\u1ea7n tra d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p,&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":930,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[43],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-1899","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin-moi-nhat"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1899","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/